Reasoning: The paper deals with computational complexity results for the quantified constraint satisfaction problem, as well as algebraic properties of idempotent polymorphisms of certain digraph classes. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Computational Complexity (cs.CC), Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
